      <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700"><td class="py-2">Multimodal (video/image/audio)</td><td class="py-2"><strong>Gemini</strong> — native multimodal from ground up</td></tr>
      <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700"><td class="py-2">Google ecosystem integration</td><td class="py-2"><strong>Gemini</strong> — Gmail, Docs, Drive, Maps</td></tr>
      <tr class=""><td class="py-2">Safety & reliability</td><td class="py-2"><strong>Claude</strong> — most refusal-aware, fewer hallucinations</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
